        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "BRASS PIN PUNCH SET DIAMETER: 1/16\", 3/32\", 1/8\", 5/32\", 3/16\", 7/32\", 1/4\", 5/16\"",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "BENEFIT AND USES: Pin punches are used to form an impression of the tip on a work piece to better drive objects, such as nails or tacs through the object being worked on.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "PRECISION PUNCH TOOL SET: brass pin punches are great for accurately and precisely punching materials out of wood, ideal for crafting and home improvement projects including woodworking",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "STORAGE POUCH INCLUDED: Brass punch set come with convenient PVC carrying pouch to store and organize your tools when not in use. Entire set easily fits inside most tool belt pockets, tool boxes and storage crafting organizers",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Ideal for professionals and hobbyists; whether for professional gunsmiths, woodworkers, or DIY enthusiasts, this brass pin punch set is an essential tool for precise and safe work",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
