        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "The Universal Tool 8Pc Brass Pin Punch Set Hobby Craft are handy tools to accurately and precisely tap or punch objects out or away from a gun or wood. <br/><br/>A punch is a hard metal rod with a shaped top at one end and a blunt butt at the other, which is usually struck by a hammer. Pin punches are typically used with ball-peen hammers to either drive objects, such as nails or to form an impression of the tip on a work piece.<br/><br/>The diameters of the punches in this set are 1/16\", 3/32\", 1/8\", 5/32\", 3/16\", 7/32\", 1/4\", and 5/16\". To make this set even better, Univeral Tool provides a convenient and durable storage pouch so that organization and transportation of your punches very convenient.<br/><br/>We are sure that you will be able to enjoy this Universal Tool 8PC Brass Pin Punch Set for all of your crafting, woodwork, and DIY needs.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
